com.mobius.vdrapi
Class PageLanguageType

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--com.mobius.vdrapi.PageLanguageType
public final class PageLanguageType
extends Object

The PageLanguageType class enumerates the available page language formats, as supported by the OutputFormatDecisionTable class and the CreatePageGroupCommand command.

See Also:
CreatePageGroupCommand, OutputFormatDecisionTable
